net.proteusframework.core.locale.xml

Class StaticKeyDataConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.locale.xml.StaticKeyDataConfig

  • public final class StaticKeyDataConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    StaticKey data configuration. This config file can be passed to LocaleSource implementations that support it to initialized the locale source with LocalizedObject data, such as text.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
